snippet.textDisplay:
To me, Selena may not be the best singer with the best vocal, but she is such a great influencer. I love the way she talks, the way she thinks and the way she expresses her thoughts. She just sounds so well-educated and kindhearted.

And she chooses songs that just really fit her vocal and voice. I mean, Bad Liar, Fetish and Wolves are all really amazing songs. They are catchy but not boringly catchy and cheaply made. She does have good taste in music. If you haven’t listened to her Revival album, go listen to the tracks Sober and Perfect. They are so amazing.
